Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
gui_get_schematic(25.10)                              gui_get_schematic(25.10)

Name
       gui_get_schematic  -  Gets  the  name of the current (active) schematic
       view

Syntax
       gui_get_schematic

       [-help]

       [-current  | -all ]

       Gets the name of the current (active) schematic view. If -all is speci-
       fied, returns the name of all open schematic views.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the gui_get_schematic command.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man  command:
              man gui_get_schematic.

       -all   Gets the names of all open schematic views.

       -current
              Gets the name of the current active schematic view.

